  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_159",
    "english": "Among the humans who have immigrated to the Demon Realm, they have taken the place of officers in an evil demonic cult. Learning magic that stimulates the mind, they provoke cultists to create a fanatical atmosphere, and provide special effects during a speech at the cult.",
